snippet.title: Dynasty Warriors 9 Empires - Opening Scene
snippet.description:
Dynasty Warriors 9 Empires is a new release in the Empires series, featuring a mix of thrilling action and country capturing simulation. Experience the human drama of the Three Kingdoms in a way only Empires can provide. Fight exciting Castle Sieges and manipulate the country's Politics. Welcome to the Empires experience!

Support My Channel Here:
www.youtube.com/LuentrixGames/join

-Don't forget to subscribe for upcoming videos! 
-If you like what you see drop me a like and a comment :D 
-Thank you for watching!
